trans-unit.source: Represents a read-only collection of the keys of a <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyDictionary`2" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyDictionary`2" /> 对象的键的只读集合。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 作为集合中元素的复制目标位置的一维数组。

trans-unit.source: The array must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: 该数组的索引必须从零开始。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中从零开始的索引，在此处开始复制。
